Counter Challenge is a coding exercise for the Cox Automotive interview process.

# Purpose
    Counter Challenge takes a string from the command line as input and returns a formatted version of the string where each word is printed with its first letter, the number of distinct charcters between the first and last letter, and then the last letter

# Setup and Run
    -Navigate to the project folder in your terminal and run
        python main.py ~insert input text here~
    ex. python main.py It was many and many a year ago

# Testing
    -Navigate to the project folder in your terminal and run
        python main.py RunTest

